<figureCitation id="F9AC2A137D4BFF8AFF74F8DEFC64F8E6" box="[159,960,1801,1828]" captionStart="FIGURES 45" captionStartId="233.[151,264,1756,1781]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1719]" captionTargetId="figure@233.[182,1406,166,1736]" captionTargetPageId="233" captionText="FIGURES 45a–45n. Facies of Solariola gestroi species group: 45a—S. gestroi (A. &amp; F. Solari, 1923) ♂ holotype; 45b—S. fraterna Baviera, 2015 ♂ holotype; 45c—S. angelinii Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45d—S. cajetanibelloi Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45e—S. calida Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♀ holotype; 45f—S. diottii Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♀ holotype; 45g—S. fancelloi Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45h—S. normanna Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45i—S. obsoleta Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45j—S. poggii Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♀ holotype; 45k—S. sbordonii Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♀ holotype; 45l—S. tedeschii Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45m—S. venusta Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holotype; 45n—S. zoiai Bellò, Osella &amp; Baviera sp.n. ♂ holo- type." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3469311" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3469311/files/figure.png" pageId="95" pageNumber="96">
